text: Tony Magnusson (born February 23, 1963) is a Swedish professional skateboarder and coowner of Osiris Shoes. Magnusson was born in Tyres√∂, located in Stockholm, Sweden. Magnusson started his career in 1983. He was a rider in the United States for the Uncle Wiggley team. Osiris was founded in 1996, and produces technical footwear for skateboarders.
